result.name: MTHFR gene polymorphism association with psoriatic arthritis risk in psoriasis
result.description: This project was conducted at the Department of Dermatology, Huashan Hospital, Fudan University, Shanghai, China, between 1 April 2015 and 15 October 2018. The project Coordinator is Kexiang Yan from Huashan Hospital.
